data.description: This spacious 4-bed, 2-bath Ashton Woods home features a unique 1.5-story plan. All bedrooms with new carpet are on the first floor, while a versatile second-floor flex or game room awaits. Enjoy upgrades like custom lighting, a rustic wood wall in the dining area, and a large island kitchen with gas appliances, tiled backsplash, and a breakfast bar. Crown molding and hardwood floors enhance the open living/kitchen/dining area, with a formal dining room (currently an office). The primary suite offers a separate shower, tub, and walk-in closet.    Outside, an oversized covered patio is ideal for entertaining and ready for your outdoor kitchen. Extra storage is provided by a 2.5-car garage and a walk-in attic. HOA amenities include gyms, pools, and jogging trails. Minutes from Bridgeland Lakeland Village and Towne Lake shopping/dining. No history of flooding.
